I '''Max Planck''' (Abril 23, 1858 &ndash; Octubri 4, 1947) metung yang [[Germany|Aleman]] [[physicist]]. Makikilala ya bilang mitatag keng [[quantum mechanics|quantum theory]], ampong metung kareng pekamaulagang physicists na ning pang20 dilanu o siglu. I Planck mirinan yang galal a [[Nobel Prize keng Physics]] inyang 1918.


